{"tid":2372874,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"不愧是地表最強老爸！《捍衛救援》拯救票房不遺餘力　連《神力女超人1984》也被打敗？","createTime":"2021-01-20T04:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T08:18:17.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e6d7e7314fee1fb17db790ec46949da57788359b","tid":2372874,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.toy-people.com/?p=59010_0119&amp;fbclid=IwAR0BFC2yxlW8_8cotwKV7648fI1MqjEplDHP57glhwPAyv8jocj9GlX3gAI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D59010_0119%26fbclid%3DIwAR0BFC2yxlW8_8cotwKV7648fI1MqjEplDHP57glhwPAyv8jocj9GlX3gAI&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmejDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=a1e6673d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.toy-people.com/?p=59010_0119&amp;fbclid=IwAR0BFC2yxlW8_8cotwKV7648fI1MqjEplDHP57glhwPAyv8jocj9GlX3gAI</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161102928863.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161102928863.jpg&h=bcde054b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年受到病毒肆虐，為此而推遲、中斷的電影多不勝數，電影市場裡一股鬱悶之氣揮之不去，所幸在2021年1月中，有「地表最強老爸」之稱的連恩尼遜（Liam Neeson）主演最新動作鉅片《捍衛救援》（The Marksman），為整個產業打開第一道曙光。 <br />\n<br />\n《捍衛救援》於上週五在全美上映，得利於1月18日馬丁&middot;路德&middot;金紀念日的連續假期，僅僅四天就拿下了票房370萬美元，打敗了《神力女超人1984》（Wonder Woman 1984）的冠軍紀錄，一舉登頂為2021年首部新片票房冠軍。這是第三部連恩尼遜為開路影業（Open Road Films）奪下票房冠軍的電影，另外兩部為2011年的《即刻獵殺》（The Grey），以及去年十月中上映的《倒數反擊》（Honest Thief）。 <br />\n<br />\n《捍衛救援》由《美國狙擊手》（American Sniper）、《會計師》（The Accountant）的團隊製作，外國網友在討論區裡多給予正面評價，認為其上有著其他動作經典大片的特質，諸如《險路勿近》（No Country for Old Men）、《藍波：最後一滴血》（Rambo: Last Blood）、《羅根》（Logan）等等，其精彩程度十分值得期待，而台灣也即將於本月20號上映。 <br />\n<br />\n雖然「地表最強老爸」又再次救援票房成功，但也不禁讓人擔心，連恩尼遜究竟還能救援多久呢？畢竟他老人家在今年就要滿69歲了，為此，連恩尼遜在《捍衛救援》訪談時給出了令人滿意的回答：「在完成今年度幾部電影之前，我都會繼續，大不了用個助行器再上。」"},{"pid":"4f2327d8d581d0e05062e99f6db4f8c5996987f3","tid":2372874,"uid":24853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:58:16.000Z","msg":"ww1984好悶"},{"pid":"acf8eb21a807c8b175c5570b885163cdd1ee48ca","tid":2372874,"uid":20224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"Lampard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691daf3dc418fb385a5dbe17ba29e4812b9ec579","tid":2372874,"uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T05:02:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lEBPNi4bEbc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlEBPNi4bEbc&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmejDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=50b52592\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lEBPNi4bEbc</a>"},{"pid":"f2a845967858f8ceb45f84316b74a876770b1aff","tid":2372874,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:18:17.000Z","msg":"😁"}]}